Replaces: udev-config-sidux (<< 0.11)
Description: custom udev configurations for udev
 Configure PCI IDs and udev events needed by aptosid.
 .
 This also provides xorg.conf.d snippets to enable advanced touchpad features
 for:
  - synaptics
  - alps
  - elantech
  - appletouch

